videos.description: Rutgers guard Jacob Young drives into the paint and loses his defender with a ball fake before dropping in the lefty floater.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Young puts defender on skates with sweet ball fake) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Young puts defender on skates with sweet ball fake

videos.description: After a hot start, Jacob Young gets a steal on defense and rises up for a dunk, but his attempt bounces off the front of the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Rutgers' Young denied by the rim) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Rutgers' Young denied by the rim

videos.description: Geo Baker draws a help defender and sends a no-look pass to Montez Mathis for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baker delivers no-look dime for Rutgers and-1) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Baker delivers no-look dime for Rutgers and-1

videos.description: Jalen Smith gets the ball in the post and spins around Shaq Carter to create space for an easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maryland's Smith spins around defender to score) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Maryland's Smith spins around defender to score

videos.description: Geo Baker drives to the rim and rises up for a two-handed slam to get Rutgers fans on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baker glides in for Rutgers jam) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Baker glides in for Rutgers jam

videos.description: Jacob Young dishes to a cutting Montez Mathis, who elevates to throw down a tomahawk slam over Jalen Smith.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mathis throws down the hammer for Rutgers) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Mathis throws down the hammer for Rutgers

videos.description: After Rutgers' 78-67 win over No. 9 Maryland, fans at Rutgers Athletic Center storm the court to celebrate the upset victory.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Rutgers fans storm court after win over No. 9 Maryland) 2020/03/03
